{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><div class=\"_page_ _page_2\">\n<h2>均香餅家推出即叫即製炸三文治！</h2>\n<p>均香餅家又有新搞作！推出全新即叫即製炸三文治，提供鮮忌廉$16、蛋沙律$16、開心果$25及黑芝麻（5月中推出）四款口味，每款都塞爆餡，外脆內軟，口感超豐富。暫時星期六日限定，今個周末去試啦！</p>\n<p>均香餅家<br/>\n地址：深水埗北河街203號地舖<br/>\n電話：27770 719<br/>\n營業時間：星期一至日 08:30 – 22:00<br/>\nIG：@kwanhongbakery</p>\n<img alt=\"0\" data-src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/177709683009418025_201859632769ec587eb0405.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"478\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/wp-content/themes/bucket/theme-content/images/default.jpg\" width=\"960\">(圖片來源：官方圖片)\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T06:02:29.641091+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":202,"images":1,"source":"WeekendHK","fallback":"none"}}